{"id": 59712, "date": "2025-09-25T04:00:39", "date_gmt": "2025-09-25T11:00:39", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59712"}, "modified": "2026-06-01T16:31:36", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-01T23:31:36", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-25-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/25/kingdom-of-days-september-25-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 25"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band is in residence at the Student Prince in Asbury Park.</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Born to Run Tour to the Auditorium Theater in Chicago. Check out video from the show below, but note that the footage was shot on Super-8 film and is silent.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/726QdONZyVo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9NqlQ5-fzE8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12923\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-09-25/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1975-09-25.jpg?fit=499%2C435&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"499,435\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-09-25\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1975-09-25.jpg?fit=499%2C435&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12923 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1975-09-25.jpg?resize=499%2C435&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1975-09-25.jpg?w=499&amp;ssl=1 499w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1975-09-25.jpg?resize=300%2C262&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce brings the Darkness Tour to Boston for a single show at Boston Garden.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4485\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0925/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0925.jpg?fit=600%2C566&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"600,566\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0925\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0925.jpg?fit=600%2C566&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4485 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0925.jpg?resize=600%2C566&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"566\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0925.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1978-0925.jpg?resize=300%2C283&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Cats on a Smooth Surface on stage at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park. At the end of their set, the band sings &#8220;Happy Birthday&#8221; to the newly 33-year-old Bruce.</p>\n<div id=\"v-29gtxmdA-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/29gtxmdA?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play &#8220;Spirit in the Night&#8221; for the last time for eight years at their second of two Born in the U.S.A. shows at Buffalo Memorial Auditorium.</p>\n<div id=\"v-D5KXaY9y-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/D5KXaY9y?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4493\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-0925/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?fit=1114%2C558&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1114,558\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-0925\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?fit=758%2C380&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4493 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?resize=758%2C380&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?w=1114&amp;ssl=1 1114w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?resize=768%2C385&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0925.jpg?resize=1024%2C513&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a surprise guest appearance with U2 at their JFK Stadium show in Philadelphia. Their performance of &#8220;Stand By Me&#8221; is professionally filmed for the band&#8217;s\u00a0<em>Rattle and Hum</em> documentary but does not make the final cut. Both local papers cover Bruce&#8217;s surprise guest appearance but I suspect only one of them actually witnessed it. (Guess which one.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IYP0MprfnVU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21424\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-09-25b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?fit=1952%2C1404&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1952,1404\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600531054&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-09-25b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?fit=758%2C546&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21424 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?resize=758%2C545&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"545\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?w=1952&amp;ssl=1 1952w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?resize=1024%2C737&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?resize=768%2C552&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25b.jpg?resize=1536%2C1105&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21423\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-09-25a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?fit=2431%2C982&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2431,982\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600530983&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-09-25a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?fit=758%2C306&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21423 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=758%2C306&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?w=2431&amp;ssl=1 2431w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=300%2C121&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=1024%2C414&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=768%2C310&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=1536%2C620&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?resize=2048%2C827&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1987-09-25a.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new touring band play their second of three World Tour 1992 shows at the L.A. Sports Arena.</p>\n<div id=\"v-nWtbJdch-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/nWtbJdch?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1996:\u00a0</strong>Bruce surprises the audience at his solo acoustic show in Akron by giving the usual opener &#8220;The Ghost of Tom Joad&#8221; a rest and instead playing a cover of Woody Guthrie&#8217;s &#8220;Tom Joad.&#8221; Mid-set, Bruce plays &#8220;Shut Out the Light&#8221; for the first time in over a decade. This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W8E6uGwkVD4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDW8E6uGwkVD4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band close out their six-night stand in Philadelphia with a killer set list, opening with their first performance of &#8220;Incident on 57th Street&#8221; in 19 years and featuring a rare &#8220;New York City Serenade&#8221; and a show-closing &#8220;Raise Your Hand.&#8221; This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UF1WY6t2UhU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hXxq3HXydIU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=tra