/kingdom-of-days-november-19-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59712, "position": 1}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: November 19", "author": "Ken", "date": "November 19, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this significant date: Bruce pays tribute to Frank Sinatra on his 80th birthday, the Blood Brothers EP is released, and Danny Federici plays his final full show. Much more inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/bloodbrothers.png?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/bloodbrothers.png?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/bloodbrothers.png?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 62409, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/21/kingdom-of-days-november-21-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 59712, "position": 2}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: November 21", "author": "Ken", "date": "November 21, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce releases his eleventh studio album, The Ghost of Tom Joad. Plus: the Seeger Sessions Tour wraps up, the return of forgotten classic \"Song for Orphans,\" and Bruce plays his first ever show in Sweden. More highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/tomjoad.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/tomjoad.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=35